divs: Sighting DetailsLooking up and to the east a bit I noticed a star like object moving across the sky south to north the sun was not up yet and i could see the sun shinning of of it . all of a sudden it went out and 10 seconds later I could see it moving again then it started to slow down and moved across the sky slower and slower until it stoped .I watched it as long as I could unti I could not stand the pain in my neck . I was on my deck and watching the last bit of night sky befor the sun came up . after it went out and came back on and was slowing down I was waving at it and I felt happy to see it
Summary: I was watching the sky a star like object was moving across the sky south to north
